<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>線上訂單資料新增 - addOnlineOrder.jsp</title>

<style>
  table#table-1 {
	background-color: #CCCCFF;
    border: 2px solid black;
    text-align: center;
  }
  table#table-1 h4 {
    color: red;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1px;
  }
  h4 {
    color: blue;
    display: inline;
  }
</style>

<style>
  table {
	width: 450px;
	background-color: white;
	margin-top: 1px;
	margin-bottom: 1px;
